profile: CC Underground is in buisness for over 23 years installing water,sewer,electrical lines for both Commercial and residential plowing,trenching but specializing in trenchless utility installation using Directional Drilling.We do everything from plowing conduit for landscape lighting to commercial parking lot lighting to drilling lake fed water lines to your house or cottage. We also do geothermal loop instals from vertical to open cut or lake loops. See our website for more info or please call to set up an onsite appointment or quote.
